msgid "The edit screen lets you correct the participant email and the form's custom-field values, and manage the linked WordPress user and the LGPD consent record. Identity and integrity fields are read-only: submission id, date, status, magic-link token, IP, CPF/RF and the auth code (so a certificate can never be silently re-pointed)."
